#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: simply-webp.php includes/admin.php:243 includes/admin.php:244
#: includes/admin.php:307
msgid "Simply WebP"
msgstr "Simply WebP"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: simply-webp.php
msgid "https://github.com/tanu-pom/simply-webp"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin
#: simply-webp.php
msgid ""
"Convert new uploads and your existing media library to WebP in place, and "
"update the references in your content. A simple, single-format approach to "
"lighter images."
msgstr ""

#. Author of the plugin
#: simply-webp.php
msgid "tanupom"
msgstr ""

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: simply-webp.php
msgid "https://github.com/tanu-pom"
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin.php:63
msgid "Conversion settings"
msgstr "変換設定"

#: includes/admin.php:70
msgid "WebP quality (JPEG)"
msgstr "WebP 品質（JPEG）"

#: includes/admin.php:79
msgid "PNG"
msgstr "PNG"

#: includes/admin.php:87
msgid "Metadata"
msgstr "メタデータ"

#: includes/admin.php:95
msgid "Reference replacement"
msgstr "参照差し替え"

#: includes/admin.php:102
msgid "Additional post types"
msgstr "追加する投稿タイプ"

#: includes/admin.php:139
msgid ""
"Reference replacement rewrites old image URLs in post_content to the new ."
"webp URLs after conversion. By default it scans posts, pages, attachments, "
"and revisions. Use the field below to add custom post types that also "
"contain image URLs."
msgstr ""
"参照差し替えは、変換後に本文中の旧画像 URL を新しい .webp URL に書き換えま"
"す。既定では投稿・固定ページ・添付ファイル・リビジョンが対象です。画像 URL を"
"含むカスタム投稿タイプがあれば、下のフィールドで追加してください。"

#: includes/admin.php:176
msgid "No public custom post types are registered on this site."
msgstr "このサイトには公開カスタム投稿タイプが登録されていません。"

#: includes/admin.php:190
msgid ""
"Each checked post type is added to the URL replacement scan in addition to "
"the defaults."
msgstr ""
"チェックした投稿タイプは、既定の対象に加えて URL 差し替えのスキャン対象になり"
"ます。"

#: includes/admin.php:202
msgid ""
"1–100. Higher means better quality but larger files. Default 80. Applies to "
"lossy (JPEG) conversion."
msgstr ""
"1〜100。大きいほど高品質ですがファイルも大きくなります。既定値は 80。ロッシー"
"（JPEG）変換に適用されます。"

#: includes/admin.php:216
msgid ""
"Encode PNG as lossless WebP (keeps transparency, avoids fringing on logos "
"and text)"
msgstr ""
"PNG をロスレス WebP で変換する（透過を保持し、ロゴや文字のにじみを防ぎます）"

#: includes/admin.php:231
msgid ""
"Strip image metadata (EXIF) — smaller files and no leaking of GPS location "
"data"
msgstr ""
"画像のメタデータ（EXIF）を除去する — ファイルが軽くなり、GPS 位置情報の漏洩も"
"防げます"

#: includes/admin.php:278
msgid "Scanning…"
msgstr "棚卸し中…"

#: includes/admin.php:279
msgid "Converting…"
msgstr "変換中…"

#: includes/admin.php:280
msgid "Replacing references…"
msgstr "参照差し替え中…"

#: includes/admin.php:281
msgid "Done"
msgstr "完了"

#: includes/admin.php:282
msgid "An error occurred."
msgstr "エラーが発生しました"

#. translators: 1: number converted, 2: total, 3: number remaining, 4: number of URL pairs accumulated.
#: includes/admin.php:284
#, php-format
msgid "Converting %1$d / %2$d (remaining %3$d, map %4$d)"
msgstr "変換中 %1$d / %2$d（残り %3$d / マップ %4$d 件）"

#. translators: 1: number converted, 2: total, 3: number of old-to-new URL pairs accumulated.
#: includes/admin.php:286
#, php-format
msgid "Done — %1$d / %2$d (%3$d old-to-new URL pairs accumulated)"
msgstr "完了 — %1$d / %2$d（旧→新 URL マップ %3$d 件を蓄積）"

#: includes/admin.php:311
msgid ""
"This server’s Imagick build cannot output WebP, so conversion is unavailable."
msgstr "このサーバの Imagick は WebP 出力に対応していません。変換できません。"

#: includes/admin.php:318
msgid "Settings saved."
msgstr "設定を保存しました。"

#: includes/admin.php:327
msgid "Save settings"
msgstr "設定を保存"

#: includes/admin.php:333
msgid "1. Inventory (scan for reference locations)"
msgstr "1. 棚卸し（参照箇所の調査）"

#: includes/admin.php:334
msgid ""
"Scans where image URLs are used across post content, meta, and options. "
"Nothing is modified."
msgstr ""
"画像 URL が本文・メタ・オプションのどこに使われているかを調べます（書き換えは"
"行いません）。"

#: includes/admin.php:336
msgid "Run inventory"
msgstr "棚卸しを実行"

#: includes/admin.php:340
msgid "2. Bulk WebP conversion"
msgstr "2. 一括 WebP 変換"

#. translators: %d: number of unconverted attachments.
#: includes/admin.php:345
#, php-format
msgid "Unconverted images (JPEG / PNG): %d"
msgstr "未変換の画像（JPEG / PNG）: %d 件"

#: includes/admin.php:350
msgid ""
"Replaces originals with WebP in place (irreversible). Back up your media "
"before running. Reference replacement is performed separately."
msgstr ""
"原本を WebP に置き換えます（不可逆）。実行前にメディアのバックアップを取って"
"ください。参照差し替えは別途行います。"

#: includes/admin.php:352
msgid "Start bulk conversion"
msgstr "一括変換を開始"

#: includes/admin.php:360
msgid "3. Replace references"
msgstr "3. 参照差し替え"

#: includes/admin.php:361
msgid ""
"Applies the accumulated “old URL → new URL” pairs to post content and "
"options. Run this after conversion."
msgstr ""
"変換で蓄積した「旧 URL → 新 URL」を本文・オプションに反映します（変換後に実"
"行）。"

#. translators: %d: number of accumulated URL pairs.
#: includes/admin.php:368
#, php-format
msgid "Accumulated URL pairs: %d"
msgstr "蓄積済みの URL ペア: %d 件"

#: includes/admin.php:374
msgid "Run reference replacement"
msgstr "参照差し替えを実行"

